<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Configurer Face ID · EchoCare</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: #F0E6D8;
            display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .card {
            background: white; border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 50px 40px; max-width: 480px; width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
            animation: slideUp 0.4s ease;
        }
        @keyframes slideUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        .icon-wrap {
            width: 100px; height: 100px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4A6FA5, #6B8FC5);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-size: 48px; margin: 0 auto 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(74,111,165,0.3);
        }
        h1 { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; color: #2C3E50; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        p { font-size: 15px; color: #777; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 32px; }
        .features {
            display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px;
        }
        .feature {
            flex: 1; background: #F5EFE6; border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 16px 12px; font-size: 13px; color: #555;
        }
        .feature .f-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .feature h4 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #2C3E50; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .buttons { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
        .btn-yes {
            padding: 16px; background: #E8895A; color: white;
            border: none; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
            display: block; transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-yes:hover { background: #d4784a; }
        .btn-no {
            padding: 14px; background: transparent; color: #4A6FA5;
            border: 1.5px solid #4A6FA5; border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none; display: block; transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-no:hover { background: #4A6FA5; color: white; }
        .skip { font-size: 12px; color: #bbb; margin-top: 16px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
    <div class="icon-wrap">👁️</div>
    <h1>Configurez votre Face ID</h1>
    <p>
        Connectez-vous en un clin d'œil grâce à la reconnaissance faciale.<br>
        Plus rapide et plus sécurisé que le mot de passe !
    </p>

    <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
            <div class="f-icon">⚡</div>
            <h4>Accès instantané</h4>
            <p>Plus besoin de mot de passe</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <div class="f-icon">🔐</div>
            <h4>Ultra sécurisé</h4>
            <p>Votre visage uniquement</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <div class="f-icon">🤖</div>
            <h4>IA avancée</h4>
            <p>Reconnaissance précise</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="buttons">
        <a href="{{ path('face_register') }}" class="btn-yes">
            📸 Oui, enregistrer mon visage
        </a>
        <a href="{{ path('admin_dashboard') }}" class="btn-no">
            ⏭️ Plus tard
        </a>
    </div>
    <p class="skip">Vous pourrez le configurer plus tard depuis le dashboard</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>